            <p>Clean, well-maintained and fully insured vehicles for every journey.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
            <h3>24/7 Support</h3>
            <p>Our team is available around the clock to assist you whenever you need us.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
            <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i>
            <h3>Affordable Rates</h3>
            <p>Competitive pricing with no hidden charges.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
